'''肯塔基州的飲食文化'''多承襲自傳統[[美國南方飲食|美國南方飲食]]。常見的晚餐菜餚包括炸鯰魚、油炸玉米餅（hushpuppy）、炸雞和鄉村煎牛排，佐以青豆、斑豆或蔬菜與豬肉慢熬而成的醬汁，搭配麵包食用。炸青茄、起司玉米粥（cheese grits）、玉米布丁、炒秋葵和餃食等也是普遍的肯塔基州佳餚<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hallsontheriver.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-15 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507012709/https://hallsontheriver.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ramseysdiners.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-15 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228190957/http://ramseysdiners.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mountain-breeze.com/kitchen/kentucky/index.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2008-12-06  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080926112128/http://www.mountain-breeze.com/kitchen/kentucky/index.html |archivedate=2008-09-26 }}</ref>。此外，肯塔基州的[[燒烤|燒烤]]料理亦獨具一格；它有別於眾南部燒烤風格，選用[[羊肉|羊肉]]為主要食材<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbbregion.org/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-15 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020161020/http://www.bbbregion.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.louisvillehotbytes.com/ole-hickory-pit-old-western-kentucky-tradition |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-15 |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324005325/http://www.louisvillehotbytes.com/ole-hickory-pit-old-western-kentucky-tradition |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了傳統南方飲食特色之外，肯塔基州也發展出獨特的地方料理，尤其是[[路易維爾_(肯塔基州)|路易維爾]]—[[熱布朗三明治|熱布朗三明治]]和[[德比三角派|德比三角派]]的發源地（雖然後者和傳統南方甜點[[胡桃派|胡桃派]]也很類似）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.brownhotel.com/dining/hot-brown.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2006-12-18 |archive-date=2007-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070823065032/http://www.brownhotel.com/dining/hot-brown.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.derbypie.com/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2011-10-15 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227071042/https://derbypie.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

